{"tid":586681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨及經民聯不同意預算案派錢","createTime":"2018-03-09T17:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T18:43:08.000Z","uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a75d85cb3160791249b680c00ff1e154e9379a6","tid":586681,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民主黨及經民聯不同意預算案派錢</span></strong><br />\n2018-01-20 HKT 08:54<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波將於下月公布《財政預算案》，對於派錢建議，民主黨及經民聯均不同意。民主黨立法會議員涂謹申出席本台節目時表示，預算案應集中協助沒有資產的市民，協助他們日常開支，例如公屋免租，或津貼輪候公屋超過三年人士的租金，善用財政盈餘。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯主席盧偉國出席同一節目時亦認為，與其派錢不如集中解決民生問題，例如容許租樓或買樓者免稅，支援幼兒教育，以及資助市民購買昂貴藥物，相信落實有關措施，會比直接派錢更受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨主席張宇人就認為，派錢可以刺激消費市道，令零售及飲食行業更為暢旺。"},{"pid":"b25ed40af41f5641d56e76218ca2549844f12a05","tid":586681,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"香港電台即時新聞 ：<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1376246-20180120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1376246-20180120.htm&d=uD6lAQA5miGWf9rW1QZJs%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0f6905af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1376246-20180120.htm&h=de9fcb75\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1376246-20180120.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a486895c5e944a291a198e10288be4a94682c49d","tid":586681,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">延伸閱讀：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[舊聞重溫] 民主派堅持反台獨免予人口實</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586281/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586281/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>司徒華主動向教育局建議，普通話進入香港教育</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586442/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586442/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>新民主同盟：支持維持家庭團聚單程証配額，不應視新來港人士為掠奪資源</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586422/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586422/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>泛民：認同居港一年即享綜援，支持維持家庭團聚單程証配額</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586321/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586321/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>民主黨的基本信念：我們支持香港回歸中國</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586292/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586292/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>教協葉建源：浸大生粗魯無禮不能接受，要求嚴肅處理</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586459/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586459/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>葉建源憂代繳考試費吸非學生市民報考<br />\n內地生踴躍報考DSE惹關注　葉建源：籲家長毋須過慮</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/576668/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/576668/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/584940/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/584940/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【蔡若蓮喪子】 前對手葉建源感難過 斥涼薄言論對死者不尊重</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/391149/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/391149/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大中華泛民祝賀保釣勇士成功登島　嚴正要求日本政府立即放人</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586498/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586498/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>新民主同盟：香港大部分人口俱為中國人</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586641/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586641/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9b89735a203f4d80a83a9d67ca1f1441210368d0","tid":586681,"uid":17506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"樓豬訓左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民主黨：不派錢不投贊成<br />\n2018年03月06日<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180306/20323542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link