市民購買昂貴藥物<br />\n<br />\n咁就差唔多"},{"pid":"685f5be0b9231dc9fd85e620e171735b51ebdc32","tid":586681,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f53f204082a54e4c7e064672c949b77aeda72b","tid":586681,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9b89735a203f4d80a83a9d67ca1f1441210368d0","tid":586681,"uid":17506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"樓豬訓左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民主黨：不派錢不投贊成<br />\n2018年03月06日<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180306/20323542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F20323542&d=uD6lAQA5miGWf9rW1QZJs%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9db2213d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F20323542&h=a6848501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180306/20323542</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:59:51.000Z","msg":"訓左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係話緊你民主黨冇立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初有份令香港人冇錢派，而加黎貓哭老鼠呃選票<br />\n<br />\n見陳茂波比人屌先見風轉舵，仲好意思貼出黎？<br />\n點解當初唔叫派錢呀？預算案出撚左先講有乜用呀？<br />\n當初一月個陣係咪即係反應錯民意呀？有冇道歉呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:15:26.000Z","msg":"首先我唔代表民主黨先,而民主黨今次都冇得選,都冇能力令政府決定派唔派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地已經係預算案前轉軚支持派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%232018-19%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%23&amp;suid=1975658817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Ffeatures%2Farticle%3Fq%3D%25232018-19%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%2523%26suid%3D1975658817&d=uD6lAQA5miGWf9rW1QZJs%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=65194e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%232018-19%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%23&amp;suid=1975658817</a><br />\n其次根本個個政治人物都係咁牆頭草架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係泛民至少肯聽市民意見,而唔係政府話乜就乜<br />\n<br />\n你想表達對佢地不滿係冇問題,只係唔好咁偏頗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ea27c78ef5a018b2edafe88d2c0d65c34b20fb","tid":586681,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbb4621e2c9e0621eebae67b7fd6fbb6f51bca6d","tid":586681,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先我唔代表民主黨先,而民主黨今次都冇得選,都冇能力令政府決定派唔派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地已經係預算案前轉軚支持派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%232018-19%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%23&amp;suid=1975658817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Ffeatures%2Farticle%3Fq%3D%25232018-19%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%2523%26suid%3D1975658817&d=uD6lAQA5miGWf9rW1QZJs%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=65194e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%232018-19%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%23&amp;suid=1975658817</a><br />\n其次根本個個政治人物都係咁牆頭草架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係泛民至少肯聽市民意見,而唔係政府話乜就乜<br />\n<br />\n你想表達對佢地不滿係冇問題,只係唔好咁偏頗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泛民冇能力直接介入政府決策。但作為反對派，係咪至少應該發聲，就算做戲都應該爭取一下？泛民不但冇為香港主流民意講過半句，是為失職。<br />\n<br />\n但不突止，泛民一直都鍾意講「公共財政」、「長遠規劃」、「幫最有需要既人」之類既懶理性閪話。倒行逆施反對派錢。即使佢地係預算案前轉軚，都無非係群情洶湧，怕眾怒難犯而見風轉舵。身為反對派，淪落到同陳茂波同一立場，醜唔醜？<br />\n<br />\n至於你話個個政治人物都係牆頭草，岩。但我要選一條牆頭草，我希望我條草係真心靠我依邊牆，而唔係背向民意反市民骨，逆風而行以為自己好理性好有型，然後又死死地氣痴返過黎。<br />\n<br />\n我都同意泛民會肯聽市民意見，但要係比市民懲罰完少緊幾個議席之後先聽。"},{"pid":"f64a8de73fbfaac67e7623bf7d9031b8737611a7","tid":586681,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:43:08.000Z","msg":"等睇補選販民全滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}